task.summary: Major re-sync with danny's personal toolkit.
Very early stage topological graph stuff. Lots of cleanup here and there.
Changes to workspace.xml file as a result of using this project's src directories as content roots in other IntelliJ projects.
Implement a ValidatedJTextField class that makes it easier to manage the validation of JTextField values.
Commit and post an irrelevant change to ...MyExploreSSL. The real purpose of this is to make sure that I didn't screw anything up in my attempts to create a new project that referenced this project.
Cleanup copyright formatting. Possibly some other minor (probably textual cleanup) changes.
Make the TreeCounter class more flexible by changing the TreeCounter( TreeCounter<K> ) constructor to take a Counter<K> instead of a TreeCounter<K>.
First commit of the Pepys event handler. Lots of cleanup here and there.

Early check-in of packers modules (not ready for prime time). First commit and push of Pepys (event mechanism that uses Java's strong, weak and zombie references to assist in managing the lifecycle of event listeners). Minor cleanup elsewhere.
Snapshot time. Working mostly on the v2 unpacker. Still trying to get the distinction between instance ids and packing ids exactly right.
